m_q.target_metric: count of games played in October
sub_questions: Which rows have dates in October?
How many rows match the October filter?

unit_annotations.Date: string representation of date (Month Day format)
unit_annotations.Attendance: number of people (string with comma separator)

format_notes: Date column contains month name and day number
Some entries have special notes in parentheses for Site and Opponent columns
Attendance contains comma-separated numbers in quotes

constraints: Date must be parseable to identify month
Only count games where Date starts with 'October'
derived_filters: Filter rows where Date column starts with 'October'
output_format_requirements: Return single integer representing count of October games
